{"tid":2119493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【美中角力】美日澳南海聯合軍演　公布照片秀軍力","createTime":"2020-07-22T06:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T07:04:48.000Z","uid":3873,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b43da38a82c8b8f46957947c8baae95698206606","tid":2119493,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:38:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/column/article/860/rnews/20200721/1770708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F860%2Frnews%2F20200721%2F1770708&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=55588b89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F860%2Frnews%2F20200721%2F1770708&h=cc565ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/column/article/860/rnews/20200721/1770708</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JMSDF_PAO/status/1285481911419166721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJMSDF_PAO%2Fstatus%2F1285481911419166721&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=4d35f2b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJMSDF_PAO%2Fstatus%2F1285481911419166721&h=e9601d2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JMSDF_PAO/status/1285481911419166721</a><br />\n<br />\n美國海軍「雙航母」上周同時現身南海之後，兵分二路分別在南海與印度洋進行聯合軍演，雷根號打擊群與日本海上自衛隊、澳洲海軍在菲律賓附近海域舉行三國聯合軍演&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n美日澳三國演習從19日起至23日舉行，美軍宣稱，與印太區域的盟國合作是例行演習，加強美國對區域穩定、並維護印太地區自由、開放的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n美國雷根號航空母艦打擊群包括第5艦載機聯隊、飛彈巡洋艦安提坦號（USS Antietam），勃克級飛彈驅逐艦馬斯廷號（USS Mustin），澳洲則派出兩棲攻擊艦坎培拉號、霍巴特號、史都華號、阿蘭達號、天狼星號等5艘軍艦。日本則派出秋月級驅逐艦照月號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBtsCm4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBtsCm4.jpg&h=ce0c19bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e646931b4b5977967947fa7b2720963ae1adfcf","tid":2119493,"uid":15948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:39:55.000Z","msg":"射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27cc30deb3dfa2ae6ff49c780bc30d874df8749c","tid":2119493,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"美日澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支共點? <br />\n支朝伊? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9cf127e93520f6b9b597ea2ce688325d2fed38","tid":2119493,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X1prSW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX1prSW4.jpg&h=5c90736c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6CJaJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6CJaJK.jpg&h=0a74385c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0c993c034128f6e719680ba1c525e6d11fa7bc5","tid":2119493,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f340cedbf4d65e393ef7a878dabb53dfdc6559db","tid":2119493,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e42cbb147f0ecb05bf257be006accf4fa349605","tid":2119493,"uid":81399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"型到拍電影咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/ha